{"tid":464516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鏗鏘集】兩年前投共，歐陽廣榮今日下場............","createTime":"2017-11-10T15:04:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T04:44:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":68,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"702e1631a0292882d8bb672cf89def7c6aaea925","tid":464516,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"2015年2月播出一集《鏗鏘集》以「青春的眼淚」為題，探討「雨傘革命」後香港青年所面對之困境。[5]當中節目訪問一位加入了建制派的年青人歐陽廣榮。他表示自己參加了首屆青少年軍事夏令營，之後因工作失敗加入建制派，又稱幫區議員搞地區宣傳工作是一盤「產業」，想盡快賺取第一桶金，認為自己只是「典型香港人」。他在鏡頭前言論隨即惹來各方的聲討，有人不恥他只為利益加入建制派，將香港的福祉變成他圖利的踏腳石，卻將自己的「機會主義」說得冠冕堂皇，有人更稱他為「世界級的世界仔」。<br />\n<br />\n歐陽廣榮事後在facebook回應，先指內容剪接了很多去刻意塑造他這種「人物」，更反問「香港年青人是『黃絲』的多，還是『務實』未發聲的多？」對於朋友的所謂冷言冷語，歐陽廣榮就指自己可在今次事件中，分得清誰是真心朋友。他又感慨香港人只將政治人物分為「泛民」和「共狗」，並批評「現在的人連我這樣觀點都容不下，還大放厥詞罵人，我覺得搞笑罷了」。他強調自己沒有出賣過香港人，例如對水貨走私問題自稱身同感受，對於大陸的黑心食材、毒奶粉、貪腐問題，自己作為中國人亦都咬牙切齒，又不明白嘗試了解中國就被扣上「出賣香港」的帽子。 被批評唯利是圖，歐陽廣榮又表示深信「越早財富自由就越能夠做到自己想做的事」，絕不會因為買不起樓就責怪政府。對於各界的聲討，他就指「歡迎善意的批評，不過請尊重自己人格，粗口不能解決事情」<br />\n<br />\n歐陽廣榮的前世：<br />\n【2015年青春的眼淚】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwMLOfCCT0I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgwMLOfCCT0I&d=zT4fhAPiSs3tMDcJXCJKdvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=b863972c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwMLOfCCT0I</a><br />\n<br />\n今日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/or57xdnm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2For57xdnm&h=8d74dfa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tnbuzep1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftnbuzep1&h=42724f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pe0r31in\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpe0r31in&h=e43837c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3ld76pxv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3ld76pxv&h=4755883e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kbma0whf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkbma0whf&h=ea270d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthk.HKConnection/videos/1471698606212550/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frthk.HKConnection%2Fvideos%2F1471698606212550%2F&d=zT4fhAPiSs3tMDcJXCJKdvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=4d30a04d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthk.HKConnection/videos/1471698606212550/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐陽廣榮點睇兩年前嘅自己？<br />\n「青春的苦澀」<br />\n全集重温：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-9uqcfI4iF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-9uqcfI4iF0&d=zT4fhAPiSs3tMDcJXCJKdvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=3fbaacfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-9uqcfI4iF0</a>"},{"pid":"0237cbcb6367d3df04d34152bdeabf77de3f387f","tid":464516,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5a73fc08a35385ec9579c2c67d631696792bf7","tid":464516,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529387ae776f61b224ae45bd84b5048b766551ca","tid":464516,"uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T15:19:19.000Z","msg":"歐陽廣榮：工作失敗，加入建制派想搵第一桶金   16/2/2015<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=5676494\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D5676494&d=zT4fhAPiSs3tMDcJXCJKdvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=bd4d1785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=5676494</a>"},{"pid":"6366447145845b0f2f5a64d8324fc4b8ea19a377","tid":464516,"uid":44105,"l